snippet.title: Moraff's Stones gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Moraff's Stones, Dos PC game produced by Moraffware in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/moraff-s-stones/4189/
Stones is a game where you trade precious/semiprecious stones. You continue playing until you are wiped out by your opponents.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
